{"tid":289799,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"36歲日本仔係機場女廁偷拍港龍空姐   被判即時監禁14天","createTime":"2017-06-19T09:42:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-19T12:14:46.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d7a96d04bc71120b810b36a7dc9b76046b783d10","tid":289799,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T09:42:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/17uYu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F17uYu.jpg&h=80c7c486&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170619/56849080\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170619%2F56849080&d=lDAs88%2FZOpgUNEcUdrqcvpUc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=659d0017\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170619%2F56849080&h=2813f634\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170619/56849080</a><br />\n<br />\n有易服癖好的日籍會計師今晨在香港國際機場落機後，戴上假長髮、穿著黑色短裙走入女廁格拍攝女士如廁影片，休班國泰港龍空姐見鄰格女廁有手機伸出揭發。會計師今在裁判法院認罪，被判即時監禁14天。<br />\n<br />\n被告Koyanagi Akihiko（36歲）承認一項不誠實使用電腦罪，指他在機場一號客運大樓入境大堂非禁區的女廁內，用手機偷拍女子裙底。<br />\n<br />\n辯方求情透露，被告已婚並育有小孩，在日本大學畢業後在廣州工作，被告一直有易服問題。事發時所穿的衣服在東京購買，被告落機後因一時有想法要易服因而犯案。<br />\n<br />\n案情指，女事主甫入女廁，已發現被告在內，她看到被告身型健碩但穿上裙子，已懷疑對方是易服男。當她如廁時，發現有手機在鄰格底部伸出，於是衝出截停被告及報警。警方發現被告犯案時身穿黃色外套，黑色短裙，粉紅色胸圍及內褲。"},{"pid":"5a58c8079d15d0487131c3a20a8971a5f0764b2a","tid":289799,"uid":29609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T09:50:36.000Z","msg":"監禁14天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f509f98e48900506e01b01a4fe45342d96cff715","tid":289799,"uid":2613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T09:54:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>監禁14天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0be2bf86103b0cebb24bb9f61a7096a37d4d83f3","tid":289799,"uid":21917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T10:02:25.000Z","msg":"原來呢d案咁快就判<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbc03a24982418e8865a29e7fb59ab298a19b00e","tid":289799,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T10:04:11.000Z","msg":"休班國泰港龍空姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n因管理不善而在全球最佳航空公司排名榜節節下跌的國泰航空，及其全資附屬公司國泰港龍休班空姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"218a45b90d155e511cfebc5b7b4d1bc1c66863d2","tid":289799,"uid":45857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T10:05:05.000Z","msg":"小柳明彦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"375d02d20ab2fb021ebba99c541289d6e71f298c","tid":289799,"uid":29887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T10:06:22.000Z","msg":"日本仔唔會咁<br />\n一定係支那仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bab66f14161b4303d8973e727b0687c480ab7a78","tid":289799,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T12:07:36.000Z","msg":"連日本仔都對港女有鍾情 估唔到閪口閪面一樣有market"},{"pid":"4a4d7b9ae71ab3ce4fa1eb8879a52669a0692fee","tid":289799,"uid":55568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T12:14:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>連日本仔都對港女有鍾情 估唔到閪口閪面一樣有market</blockquote><br />\n人地要套制服咋"}]}